This menu allows you to either contract or expand the length or width of
the form.  To contract the form, move the cursor to the desired location
and select the "Place" menu item.  Expanding the form is accomplished by
selecting the "Expand" menu item.

The menu commands are:

        MENU COMMANDS   SYNOPSIS
        -------------   --------
        Place           Place the selected boundary at cursor position.
                        If this will cause overlap with components on
                        the form, then the boundary will be placed as close
                        to the last component as possible.

        Expand          Expand the form by a quarter of a display screen
                        either to the right (if you are moving the right
                        border) or down (if you are moving the end of the form).

        Help            Access the Ingres Help facility.

        End             Leave this menu without doing anything.
